data.description: Gated Community. 3 bedrooms 2.5 bath. Open family room, dining room and kitchen with counter bar. On the second floor is the very large Master bedroom with large walk-in closet and spacious master bath with separate shower. Bedroom 2 and 3 share a bathroom. Refrigerator, mini blinds and garage door openers included. Very easy access to FM 1960 and I-45.
